{"title": "Web Services - How do I Activate the PRODA Device?", "body": "1.The PRODA configuration is found in More > Settings > Configuration Settings > Practice > Claiming - PRODA\n 2. Simply tick the checkbox to use the Vendor PRODA Device\n3. Make your selections on the additional Claiming options as to what your organisation requires and click Save\n\n*NOTE: Multiple practices are able to send from the same Location Code - please overwrite the Minor Site ID with the 'master' ID from your original practice at this stage.\n  For more information about these options, please see the following informational articles:\nAutomatically Submits AIR Claim\nAutomatically Submits Medicare Claims\nAutomatically Retrieves Medicare Rpt. \nRural or Remote Area"}